Interface BoundedContextBaseDescriptor

All Superinterfaces:
com.buschmais.xo.api.CompositeObject, com.buschmais.jqassistant.core.store.api.model.Descriptor

BoundedContextDescriptor
@Label("BoundedContext") public interface BoundedContextBaseDescriptor extends com.buschmais.jqassistant.core.store.api.model.Descriptor
Descriptor for bounded contexts independent of the Context Mapper, e.g. for compatibility with jMolecules.
